{"tid":1182392,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"許冠傑  - 同舟共濟","createTime":"2019-06-02T06:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-12T10:01:27.000Z","uid":45741,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d46a04dc08cb7c54d552dd458bbc6eef18d13b24","tid":1182392,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"我與你同坐這條船，無情浪把它猛捲，滿天風雨，<br />\n視野未能見，亂作一大團，不知怎算。<br />\n<br />\n既決意留在這條船，齊齊令它不遭破損，困境挑戰，<br />\n奮勇地面對，令到這條船，永不翻轉。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我心，一顆不變心，實在極不願，移民外國做二等公民，<br />\n必須抱著信心，把基礎打穩，盡力地做我本份，定能突破戰勝黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n破鏡明日定會重圓，時局定必得好轉，懷著希冀，<br />\n再創造時勢，令到這條船，永久溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我心，一顆不變心，實在極不願，移民外國做二等公民，<br />\n必須抱著信心，把基礎打穩，盡力地做我本份，定能突破戰勝黑暗。<br />\n<br />\n香港是我家，怎捨得失去它，實在極不願，移民外國做遞菜斟茶，<br />\n緊緊抱著結他，傾出這心裏話，但藉著這番話，齊齊共發洩一下，<br />\n但願日後獅子山下，人人團結，永不分化。"},{"pid":"496c4c07885f6c818dd36a9f77e0135b3d06a257","tid":1182392,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h_br1JKkQeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh_br1JKkQeA&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=bc68e5a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h_br1JKkQeA</a>"},{"pid":"3ef52ec43600bea52a8a7bbd716e700fb81587e8","tid":1182392,"uid":20368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"黎緊遊行轉song list啦？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe34d3339a01529914aff899c7bc42a71cf0fa5","tid":1182392,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T00:38:39.000Z","msg":"許冠傑唱住香港是我家走去移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6322a0b5e172f5d946425318b684b1a205188d20","tid":1182392,"uid":103914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fe34d3339a01529914aff899c7bc42a71cf0fa5","tid":1182392,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"